caption: Classic Rock, old movies! Super Staff n friendly patrons!  We had a taste off on two bourbons.  Both very good, one though was over the top! No hints, discover for yourself, great view of street and traffic below!
Nice place great atmosphere friendly staff and if you get hungry while drinking there a pizza place downstairs
Great cocktails

The bartender was amazing and very knowledgeable. He asked a couple questions and made the perfect cocktail. He will prove that making a drink is truly a craft of anticipation and skill. It's a super chill location that also happens to have amazing pizza below the bar. You can't go wrong.

Very nice place to go and relax while sipping on some bourbon and enjoying a pizza. The bartenders were very professional and it was awesome to see there skills while they made drinks in front of you. Definitely a place that does things right!
The bartenders here are legit. They take their time to craft a drink, not just to pour one. Great selection of whiskey and amazing atmosphere.
Excellent as always

One of the best nights I've had since Covid hit us all with such odd times. The staff was very safe, all CDC rules followed. Our party was very attended to and the drinks were amazing. I'll always come here first great times.
Greatservice at the upstairs bar made our anniversary.  Friendly, welcoming.  With just a little bit of cherky. Just what you wsnt in a place to eat

Great pizza, good selection of local brews and kick azz selection of bourbon. Servers and bartenders all super chill and helpful. So if you are not familiar with the makes and models to sip and shoot, this is the place to come and find what fits you in a relaxed and nonjudgmental environment.
Selection is unparalleled! Prices on some bourbons is reasonable but if you want ultra rare you are going to pay for it. Atmosphere is perfect for small groups but space is tight.
Friendly staff,a very good Old Fashioned.
Fun
Great Bourbon bar !!
Some place down the street boasts best selection of bourbon...good..more for me! And pizza is always terrific!
Awesome bar and pizza.
hd to go to bar to get order..even thought the bartenders were walking around and mixing it up...but not witing on the couch area
Very laid back atmosphere and a great spot for late night eats & drinks!  The pizza was DELICIOUS!
Great tasting drinks. Very talented and knowledgeable staff
Awesome hidden gem. Just wish there was more space.
Really comfortable and great pizza downstairs
Adorable upstairs “speakeasy” with an impressive whiskey selection and great cocktails. It was cozy and cute, and I loved that you could order pizza from downstairs to bring up.
Love this place! Laid back place to have an amazing cocktail
Minnie was an amazing bartender,  Anson was also very attentive as well. I enjoyed my time there! What a great night! I actually prefer this Wiseguy Lounge over the one in OTR!
Excellent place to go have a adult beverage.
Great place to have pizza and beers
Loved this place..small out of the way speakeasy type Bourbon Bar,above Goodfellas Pizza, pleasant, friendly, well made drinks

We come here anytime we're in Covington. Grab a giant slice of delicious pizza from down below and bring it upstairs to pair with an Old Fashioned from their huge selection of bourbon. Great bartenders and great atmosphere.
Great everytime
Great selection of Bourbons!
Amazing bourbon selection.
One of the best places in NKY to go for a cocktail.
The bartender was great. He gave me something different and he was attentive who came up to the bar first.
Amazing bartending and selection. Was very impressed with this second floor hideaway above a "by the slice" pizza spot. Would highly recommend.

Great bar. The bottom floor is a New York style pizza restaurant that is 1930's gangster themed. The pizza is good and the upstairs Wiseguy Longue is a great place to wait for your food. The bartender was enjoyable and the drinks perfect.  The place was quiet enough to have a conversation around 4 pm when I visited, unlike a loud sports bar blasting rock music over roudy customers. The interior was nicely decorated with wood to resemble a speakeasy.
O0  Wonderful craft cocktails and an immense bourbon selection!
Best whiskey sour every made here
Fun and funky...plus Za
May have a good selection but will never know. Waited 10 minutes at the bar without getting served. Picked the wrong end if  the bar and definitely wrong bartender
Awesome pizza from Goodfellas downstairs and fantastic cocktails at Wiseguys.
I love having a drink up here with my pizza
The bartenders are tremendous and very talented.  They definitely take their craft serious!
Good atmosphere. Reasonably priced drinks and they'll bring you your pizza from Goodfellas up.
Knowledgeable and friendly bartenders. The selection is great! This place has a very relaxing environment.
Best Bar I've been to. Great bartenders who will give you one of the best drinks you've ever had.

Upstairs and downstairs simply cannot be beat for the New York style pizza, breads and calzones worthy of New York ...extensive bourbon selection in the perfect cozy atmosphere of the renovated lounge ad covered outdoor patio itself. A five-star gem ..... Pizza and Bar Masters are second to none. From a regular.
Excellent cocktails!

Very cool atmosphere. Great drinks, you can always find something for everyone. There’s not a lot of space inside but there’s plenty of seating outside on their patios. Plus before you leave you can stop in downstairs at Goodfellas pizza on your way home and get a slice of handcrafted pizza. They’re big slices, but hit the spot after a night of drinks.
If you want to find a spot that is a hidden gem this is the place to go.  Has the best bourbon selection and a staff that knows every bottle.  This is a place I always take out of town guests!
I enjoy having drinks with friends and relaxing here. It has such a clean, classy and comfortable feel. The outside patio is great and perfect for a warm evening.
Nice, upscale bar

I visited the wiseguy lounge while on a business trip in Cincinnati. Excellent place to enjoy just about any bourbon or whiskey imaginable. They have some special reserves that are top notch as well. I highly recommend this place if you are a bourbon connoisseur.

This location has a fantastic whiskey selection with reasonable prices.  Their cocktails are stellar although a little on the sweet side.  The bartenders do a fantastic job of creating a show every cocktail and truly care about their cocktails.
Excellent place for legitimate craft cocktails
Speakeasy feel, craft beverages made with pride.
Great bourbon bar with great selection and staff. Make sure you grab a slice of Goodfella’s pizza on your way up!

I really enjoyed the laid back vibe in this club. I was looking for a place to meet a friend. I wanted it to be quiet enough to talk, cozy, comfortable enough to sit for a while and not outrageously priced. I looked for places around Cinci, Covington and Florence for five nights (not all evening, but at least some). I think they hit all of my goals square on the head! Had an enjoyable night. The pizza downstairs at Goodfellas smelled and looked wonderful. Will probably sample on my next visit!

Been coming here since its inception and I've never been disappointed. Some of the same staff has been around for the entire time which makes it great to see a familiar face. Great cocktails, conversation and overall experience. Be a bourbon connoisseur, try 100 unique (they have 400+) bourbons and earn a spot on the wall of fame and your own personalized glass. Try 250 and you become legend.
The most skilled bartenders in the area. Go have a cocktail. Enjoy an amazing slice of pizza.

My favorite cocktail bar in the area! The whole team in the 'Za shop and upstairs is amazing! One if the widest selections of bourbon I've seen, next to OKBB, which is really saying something. What they do with their selection is bar-none. There's an amazing amount of craftsmanship that goes into their work and one can definitely tell. From scratch syrups and unique recipes keep me coming back!
Most knowledgeable bartenders around and a fantastic atmosphere
The absolute best bourbon bar in northern Kentucky

One of the best bourbon directions in northern Kentucky or Cincinnati. All are moderately priced. Staff is fantastic and very nice. They have custom cocktails and you don't have to wait too long. Best part... Pizza below at any time.
Best cocktails in town.
Neat spot; overpriced.
The best pizza in the state of Kentucky
Holly makes a fantastic sazerac.
Fun

This is a nice bar if you want a drink that is made with attention to the details. My favorite Old Fashioned out there. The place is well kept but not a lot of seating. The out door deck is great even in the colder months. Worth stopping by, and Goodfellas pizza downstairs is some of the best.
Nice place to have a few drinks
Whole place is great. Old building gives it great ambience. Decor perfect. Comfortable with incredible array of Bourbons.
Best bourbon selection i have ever seen.
Cool atmosphere
Packed every time that I have been there.   Good selection of bourbon up stairs.
One of the best Bourbon bar's I've ever been to!
Absolutely adore this place! Best cocktails & bartenders in Cov! Try the beautician's boot, so good!
Great staff and good drinks.  Love the atmosphere.
Great bourbon selection and whiskey sours made the right way (with egg) and Kentucky mules on copper mugs.
Speak easy type atmosphere. Grab a pizza and head on up!
Moscow mule
Wonderful cocktails, bourbon and bartenders.   Sometimes it gets very crowded, I prefer to go when there are fewer people.  Grab a slice of pizza down stairs or order at the bar.
Good pizza! Huge breadsticks! Great service!
A must-visit for any and all bourbon enthusiasts ... and even those who aren't ... staff is outstanding, drinks are outstanding, pizza is excellent ... what more does one need?
Amazing drinks and the best bartenders!
One of my favorite bars in Cincinnati directly above Goodfellas. Has an outdoor patio as well. Great place to get a drink with plenty of drink options, especially bourbon
One of the best bars around, especially if you enjoy Bourbon. The bartenders are more like artists with their mixology but most importantly, the drinks taste delicious and are reasonably priced.
Great business. Top bartenders. Instant favorite
Great drinks, huge selection of bourbons. Great atmosphere. You can rent out the top level.
Always a great drink. If you don't know what you want, tell the bartender what you like and they'll bring you a winner. And hey, you can order amazing pizza from Goodfella's downstairs...bonus!
If you are just passing through town, you gotta go here. Just for one drink: the old fashioned. Watch them make it, be amazed, you won't regret it.
This place is pro level bartenders

Bourbon back room speak easy with delicious NY style pizza.  Their selection and knowledgeable staff sets this place miles ahead of any other bar in the area.  During the week it is relaxed and on the weekend it is packed.
Great drinks. Knowledgeable and polite.
Spent two months of weekends hanging out in this place.  The drinks are amazing and staff is even better.  You owe it to yourself to stop by and check it out.

Great whisk(e)y selection and fantastic cocktails crafted by some really talented bartenders who are also great for conversation. Doesn't hurt at all that it's right above a great pizza joint and you can move back and forth between the two spaces freely - even order pizza up! Add in the outdoor area and you can't find a better place to have a drink.
Fantastic drinks and atmosphere
Get in and try this place...don't worry you won't get "rubbed out". Seriously though, some tasty food offerings available here. Friendly staff too! Liz P.

I frequent this bourbon bar because the bartenders really know their liquor. If someone is unsure what they would like to drink, they will take the time to talk to learn about their tastes and then serve them drinks based on their preferences. They truly are bourbon aficionados, and are always pleasant. The outdoor space at this bar is perfect for a date, or for large groups.
